## 🗃️ Example BigQuery SQL

**Member dimension (dedupe)**
```sql
CREATE OR REPLACE TABLE `project.dataset.dim_member` AS
SELECT
  member_id,
  ANY_VALUE(first_name) AS first_name,
  ANY_VALUE(last_name)  AS last_name,
  MIN(effective_date)   AS first_effective_date,
  MAX(term_date)        AS last_term_date
FROM `project.dataset.members_raw`
GROUP BY member_id;
